//001835:     Private Sub frmMain_Load(ByVal sender As Object, _
//001836: ByVal e As System.EventArgs) Handles MyBase.Load
//001837: 
//001838:         DisplayFineControls(False)
//001839:         mPlayer.uiMode = "none"
//001840:         mPlayer.stretchToFit = True
//001841:         MPcontrols.Player = mPlayer
//001842:         MPcontrols.Volume = mPlayer.settings.volume
//001843: 
//001844:         'If CheckUpdate(True, True) Then Me.Close()
//001845: 
//001846:         LoadSettings()
//001847: 
//001848:         Dim CmdArgs As String() = Environment.GetCommandLineArgs()
//001849:         If CmdArgs.Length > 1 Then
//001850:             'Add check later to see that param /play is being passed
//001851:             Try
//001852:                 If String.Compare(Trim(CmdArgs(1)), "/play", False) = 0 Then
//001853:                     LoadMask(CmdArgs(2))
//001854:                 ElseIf String.Compare(Trim(CmdArgs(1)), "/edit", False) = 0 Then
//001855:                     Dim Filename As String = CmdArgs(2)
//001856:                     If isValidExtension(Filename) Then
//001857:                         OpenFile(Filename)
//001858:                     End If
//001859:                 End If
//001860:             Catch ex As Exception
//001861:                 'do nothing - ignore pranks ;)
//001862:             End Try
//001863:         End If
//001864: 
//001865:         mOpenFileExtender.DialogViewType = cOpenFileDialogExt.DialogViewTypes.Thumbnails
//001866: 
//001867:     End Sub
//001868: 
//001869:     Private Sub LoadSettings()
//001870: 
//001871:         Select Case mSettings.GetSetting("View", "SelectedTab")
//001872:             Case "tabJoin"
//001873:                 mainTabs.SelectedTab = tabJoin
//001874:             Case "tabSplit"
//001875:                 mainTabs.SelectedTab = tabSplit
//001876:             Case Else
//001877:                 mainTabs.SelectedTab = tabPlayer
//001878:         End Select
//001879: 
//001880:         If mSettings.GetSetting("Joining", "AutoDetect") = "True" Then
//001881:             chkAuto.Checked = True
//001882:         End If
//001883: 
//001884:         If mSettings.GetSetting("Advanced", "KeepHistory") = "True" Then
//001885:             chkKeepMRU.Checked = True
//001886:         End If
//001887: 
//001888:         If mSettings.GetSetting("Advanced", "FrameAccurate", "True") = "True" Then
//001889:             chkFrameAccurate.Checked = True
//001890:         End If
//001891: 
//001892:         If mSettings.GetSetting("View", "DialogView") = "Default" Then
//001893:             chkDialogView.Checked = False
//001894:         End If
//001895: 
//001896:         If mSettings.GetSetting("View", "WindowState") = "Maximized" Then
//001897:             Me.WindowState = FormWindowState.Maximized
//001898:         End If
//001899: 
//001900:         MPcontrols.VolBar.Value = CInt(mSettings.GetSetting("Player", "Volume", "50"))
//001901: 
//001902:         If mSettings.GetSetting("Player", "Mute") = "True" Then
//001903:             mPlayMuted = True
//001904:             MPcontrols.Mute = True
//001905:         End If
//001906: 
//001907:         If mSettings.GetSetting("Player", "OnTop", "True") = "True" Then
//001908:             chkOnTop.Checked = True
//001909:         End If
//001910: 
//001911:         If mSettings.GetSetting("Advanced", "CheckUpdate") = "True" Then
//001912:             chkUpdate.Checked = True
//001913:         End If
//001914: 
//001915:         If mSettings.GetSetting("Advanced", "BeepWhenDone") = "True" Then
//001916:             chkBeep.Checked = True
//001917:         End If
//001918: 
//001919:         LoadLangList()
//001920: 
//001921:     End Sub
//001922: 
//001923:     Private Function DirtyCheck() As Boolean
//001924: 
//001925:         If mSelsDirty Then
//001926:             If mMaskFile Then
//001927:                 If MsgBox(Replace(mTranslator.LangText(119), "{1}", mMaskFilename), MsgBoxStyle.YesNo) = MsgBoxResult.Yes Then
//001928:                     SaveMask(True)
//001929:                 End If
//001930:             Else
//001931:                 If MsgBox(mTranslator.LangText(127), MsgBoxStyle.YesNo) = MsgBoxResult.No Then
//001932:                     Return True
//001933:                 End If
//001934:             End If
//001935:         End If
//001936: 
//001937:     End Function
//001938: 
//001939:     Private Sub frmMain_Closing(ByVal sender As Object, _
//001940:     ByVal e As System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs) Handles MyBase.Closing
//001941: 
//001942:         If DirtyCheck() Then
//001943:             e.Cancel = True
//001944:         Else
//001945:             mSettings.SaveSetting("Joining", "AutoDetect", chkAuto.Checked.ToString)
//001946:             mSettings.SaveSetting("Joining", "AutoDelete", chkDel.Checked.ToString)
//001947:             mSettings.SaveSetting("Advanced", "KeepHistory", chkKeepMRU.Checked.ToString)
//001948:             mSettings.SaveSetting("Advanced", "CheckUpdate", chkUpdate.Checked.ToString)
//001949:             mSettings.SaveSetting("Advanced", "FrameAccurate", chkFrameAccurate.Checked.ToString)
//001950:             mSettings.SaveSetting("Advanced", "BeepWhenDone", chkBeep.Checked.ToString)
//001951:             mSettings.SaveSetting("Player", "Mute", MPcontrols.cMute.Pushed.ToString)
//001952:             mSettings.SaveSetting("Player", "Volume", MPcontrols.VolBar.Value.ToString)
//001953:             mSettings.SaveSetting("Player", "OnTop", chkOnTop.Checked.ToString)
//001954:             If Not chkDialogView.Checked Then
//001955:                 mSettings.SaveSetting("View", "DialogView", "Default")
//001956:             End If
//001957:             mSettings.SaveSetting("View", "WindowState", Me.WindowState.ToString)
//001958:             mSettings.SaveSetting("View", "SelectedTab", mainTabs.SelectedTab.Name)
//001959:             SaveToolMgr()
//001960:         End If
//001961: 
//001962:     End Sub
//001963: 
//001964:     Protected Overrides Sub WndProc(ByRef m As Message)

//001973:     Private Sub mnuOpen_Click(ByVal sender As System.Object, _
//001974: ByVal e As System.EventArgs) Handles mnuOpen.Click
//001975: 
//001976:         If mainTabs.SelectedTab Is tabJoin Then
//001977:             OpenFilesForJoining()
//001978:         Else
//001979:             Dim Filter As String = mStdToolMgr.ValidExtenstions(True)
//001980:             Filter = Replace(Filter, ".", "*.")
//001981:             Filter = Replace(Filter, "|", ";")
//001982: 
//001983:             dlgOpenFile.Filter = "Supported Media Files|" & Filter    '*.wmv;*.asf;*.mpg;*.mpeg;*.avi;*.rm";*.flv;*.mp3;*.wma
//001984:             dlgOpenFile.Multiselect = False
//001985:             If chkDialogView.Checked Then mOpenFileExtender.Enabled = True
//001986: 
//001987:             If dlgOpenFile.ShowDialog() = Windows.Forms.DialogResult.OK Then
//001988:                 Me.Refresh()
//001989:                 If Len(dlgOpenFile.FileName) > 0 Then
//001990:                     mMaskFile = False
//001991:                     OpenFile(dlgOpenFile.FileName)
//001992:                 End If
//001993:             End If
//001994: 
//001995:             mOpenFileExtender.Enabled = False
//001996:         End If
//001997: 
//001998:     End Sub
//001999: 
//002000:     Private Sub OpenFile(ByVal Filename As String, Optional ByVal MaskName As String = "")
//002001: 
//002002:         Waiting(True)
//002003:         Dim fi As New FileInfo(Filename)
//002004:         If UCase(fi.Extension) = ".MOVICLIP" Then
//002005:             LoadMask(Filename)
//002006:             Exit Sub
//002007:         End If
//002008: 
//002009:         mFileLoaded = False
//002010:         mInFile = Filename
//002011: 
//002012:         statMain.Text = mTranslator.LangText(96)
//002013:         Try
//002014:             If CreateHandler(fi.Extension) Then
//002015:                 mPlayer.URL = mInFile
//002016:                 mMRU.Add(Filename)
//002017:             End If
//002018:         Catch ex As Exception
//002019:             Debug.WriteLine(mTranslator.LangText(112) & vbCrLf & ex.Message)
//002020:             If Len(MaskName) > 0 Then lvPositions.Items.Clear()
//002021:             mPlayer.URL = ""
//002022:             Waiting(False)
//002023:             Exit Sub
//002024:         End Try
//002025: 
//002026:         UpdateTitle(fi.Name, MaskName)
//002027:         tFile2Split.Text = Trim(fi.Name)
//002028:         mainTabs.SelectedTab = tabPlayer
//002029: 
//002030:         UpdateEditorOptions(fi.Extension)
//002031: 
//002032:     End Sub
//002033: 
//002034:     Private Sub UpdateTitle(ByVal Movie As String, Optional ByVal Mask As String = "")
//002035:         Me.Text = "Movica - [" & Movie
//002036:         If Len(Mask) > 0 Then Me.Text += " : " & Mask
//002037:         Me.Text += "]"
//002038:     End Sub

//002071: 
//002072:     Private Sub SaveOutput(Optional ByVal _
//002073:         Mode As AbstractMediaHandler.Mode = AbstractMediaHandler.Mode.SaveSelected)
//002074: 
//002075:         If Not FinishTheList() Then Exit Sub
//002076: 
//002077:         UpdateHandlerOptions()
//002078: 
//002079:         dlgSaveFile.InitialDirectory = dlgOpenFile.InitialDirectory
//002080:         dlgSaveFile.DefaultExt = mHandler.Extension
//002081:         dlgSaveFile.FileName = ""
//002082:         dlgSaveFile.Filter = mHandler.Extension(True) + " |*" + mHandler.Extension
//002083: 
//002084:         If dlgSaveFile.ShowDialog() = Windows.Forms.DialogResult.OK Then
//002085:             Me.Refresh()
//002086: 
//002087:             Dim Filename As String = dlgSaveFile.FileName
//002088:             If Filename = mHandler.InputFile Then
//002089:                 MsgBox("Output cannot be the same as the input file")
//002090:                 Exit Sub
//002091:             End If
//002092: 
//002093:             Dim CutterPath As String
//002094:             CutterPath = System.AppDomain.CurrentDomain.BaseDirectory
//002095: 
//002096:             If Len(Filename) > 0 Then
//002097: 
//002098:                 mainTabs.SelectedTab = tabTrace
//002099:                 statMain.Text = mTranslator.LangText(72)
//002100:                 rtfTrace.Clear()
//002101: 
//002102:                 Try
//002103:                     Dim Segments As Segment() = GetSegmentArray(Mode)
//002104: 
//002105:                     If mHandler.Save(Filename, Segments, Mode) Then
//002106:                         UpdateRTF(mTranslator.LangText(87) & vbCrLf & vbCrLf, _
//002107:                             modMain.MessageType.Success)
//002108:                         ShowProcessStat(modMain.MessageType.Success)
//002109:                     Else
//002110:                         UpdateRTF(vbCrLf & "Conversion Failed !!" & vbCrLf & vbCrLf, _
//002111:                             modMain.MessageType.Failure)
//002112:                         ShowProcessStat(modMain.MessageType.Failure)
//002113:                     End If
//002114:                 Catch ex As Exception
//002115:                     MsgBox(ex.Message)
//002116:                 End Try
//002117: 
//002118:                 mSelsDirty = False
//002119:                 statMain.Text = mTranslator.LangText(23)
//002120:                 If chkBeep.Checked Then Beep()
//002121: 
//002122:             End If
//002123:         End If
//002124: 
//002125:     End Sub
//002126: 
//002127:     Private Function GetSegmentArray(ByVal Mode As AbstractMediaHandler.Mode) _
//002128:         As Segment()
//002129: 
//002130:         If lvPositions.Items.Count = 0 Then Return Nothing
//002131: 
//002132:         Dim Segments(lvPositions.Items.Count - 1) As Segment
//002133: 
//002134:         Select Case Mode
//002135:             Case AbstractMediaHandler.Mode.DeleteSelected
//002136:                 'Start from zero if the entry does not start from zero
//002137:                 Dim Offset As Integer = 1
//002138:                 If MinToSec(lvPositions.Items(0).Text) > 0 Then
//002139:                     ReDim Segments(lvPositions.Items.Count)
//002140:                     Segments(0) = New Segment
//002141:                     Segments(0).Start = 0
//002142:                     Segments(0).Finish = MinToSec(lvPositions.Items(0).Text)
//002143:                     Offset = 0
//002144:                 End If
//002145:                 Dim i As Integer
//002146:                 For i = 1 To lvPositions.Items.Count - 1
//002147:                     Segments(i - Offset) = New Segment
//002148:                     Segments(i - Offset).Start = MinToSec(lvPositions.Items(i - 1).SubItems(1).Text)
//002149:                     Segments(i - Offset).Finish = MinToSec(lvPositions.Items(i).Text)
//002150:                 Next
//002151:                 If lvPositions.Items(i - 1).SubItems(1).Text = SecToMin(Math.Round(mPlayer.currentMedia.duration, 3)) Then
//002152:                     'The tail piece is not needed
//002153:                     ReDim Preserve Segments(lvPositions.Items.Count - 1)
//002154:                 Else
//002155:                     Segments(i - Offset) = New Segment
//002156:                     Segments(i - Offset).Start = MinToSec(lvPositions.Items(i - 1).SubItems(1).Text)
//002157:                     Segments(i - Offset).Finish = Math.Round(mPlayer.currentMedia.duration, 3)
//002158:                 End If
//002159:             Case Else
//002160:                 For i As Integer = 0 To lvPositions.Items.Count - 1
//002161:                     Segments(i) = New Segment
//002162:                     Segments(i).Start = MinToSec(lvPositions.Items(i).Text)
//002163:                     Segments(i).Finish = MinToSec(lvPositions.Items(i).SubItems(1).Text)
//002164:                 Next
//002165:         End Select
//002166: 
//002167:         Return Segments
//002168: 
//002169:     End Function
//002170: 
//002171:     Private Function FinishTheList() As Boolean
//002172: 
//002173:         Dim Last As Integer = lvPositions.Items.Count - 1
//002174:         If Last < 0 Then Exit Function
//002175: 
//002176:         If lvPositions.Items(Last).SubItems.Count = 1 Then
//002177:             Dim EndPos As String
//002178:             EndPos = SecToMin(Math.Round(mPlayer.currentMedia.duration, 3))
//002179:             lvPositions.Items(Last).SubItems.Add(EndPos)
//002180:         End If
//002181:         mPlayer.Ctlcontrols.pause()
//002182: 
//002183:         UpdateSelDur()
//002184:         Return True
//002185: 
//002186:     End Function
//002187:

//002210:     Private Sub mnuImpSkip_Click(ByVal sender As System.Object, ByVal e As System.EventArgs) Handles mnuImpSkip.Click
//002211: 
//002212:         Dim lvItem As ListViewItem
//002213:         Dim SkipXml As New XmlDocument
//002214:         Dim TimeStr, TimeEnd As Double
//002215:         Dim MaxVal As Double = mPlayer.currentMedia.duration
//002216:         SkipXml.Load(mInFile & ".chapters.xml")
//002217:         If Not SkipXml Is Nothing Then
//002218:             lvPositions.Items.Clear()
//002219:             Try
//002220:                 lvItem = lvPositions.Items.Add(SecToMin(0))
//002221:                 For Each Seg As XmlNode In SkipXml.SelectNodes("cutlist/Region")
//002222:                     TimeStr = MinToSec(Seg.SelectSingleNode("start").Attributes.GetNamedItem("comment").InnerText)
//002223:                     TimeEnd = MinToSec(Seg.SelectSingleNode("end").Attributes.GetNamedItem("comment").InnerText)
//002224: 
//002225:                     'Validate
//002226:                     If (TimeStr > MaxVal) Or (TimeEnd > MaxVal) Then
//002227:                         MsgBox("This file has positions outside the extent of the movie." & vbCrLf & "Please check if you have the correct file", _
//002228:                         MsgBoxStyle.Exclamation, "Error in reading skip file")
//002229:                         Exit Try
//002230:                     End If
//002231: 
//002232:                     'Add item
//002233:                     If TimeStr > 0 Then
//002234:                         lvItem.SubItems.Add(SecToMin(TimeStr))
//002235:                         lvItem = lvPositions.Items.Add(SecToMin(TimeEnd))
//002236:                     Else
//002237:                         lvItem.Text = SecToMin(TimeEnd)
//002238:                     End If
//002239:                 Next
//002240:             Catch ex As Exception
//002241:                 Debug.WriteLine(ex.Message)
//002242:             End Try
//002243: 
//002244:             lvItem.SubItems.Add(SecToMin(MaxVal))
//002245:         End If
//002246: 
//002247:     End Sub
//002248: 
//002249:     Private Sub mnuImpComskip_Click(ByVal sender As System.Object, ByVal e As System.EventArgs) Handles mnuImpComskip.Click
//002250: 
//002251:         Dim sr As System.IO.StreamReader
//002252:         Dim Line As String, lvItem As ListViewItem
//002253:         Dim TimeStr, TimeEnd, FrameRate As Double
//002254:         Dim Temp As String()
//002255:         Dim MaxVal As Double = mPlayer.currentMedia.duration
//002256: 
//002257:         lvPositions.Items.Clear()
//002258:         Try
//002259:             sr = File.OpenText(StripExtention(mInFile) & ".txt")
//002260:             Line = Trim(sr.ReadLine)
//002261:             Temp = Split(Line, " ")
//002262:             FrameRate = Val(Temp(UBound(Temp))) / 100
//002263:             Line = sr.ReadLine
//002264: 
//002265:             lvItem = lvPositions.Items.Add(SecToMin(0))
//002266:             While sr.Peek <> -1
//002267:                 Line = sr.ReadLine()
//002268:                 Temp = Split(Line, Chr(9))
//002269:                 TimeStr = (Val(Temp(0)) - 1) / FrameRate
//002270:                 TimeEnd = (Val(Temp(1)) - 1) / FrameRate
//002271: 
//002272:                 'Validate
//002273:                 If (TimeStr > MaxVal) Or (TimeEnd > MaxVal) Then
//002274:                     MsgBox("This file has positions outside the extent of the movie." & vbCrLf & "Please check if you have the correct file", _
//002275:                     MsgBoxStyle.Exclamation, "Error in reading skip file")
//002276:                     Exit Try
//002277:                 End If
//002278: 
//002279:                 'Add item
//002280:                 If TimeStr > 0 Then
//002281:                     lvItem.SubItems.Add(SecToMin(TimeStr))
//002282:                     lvItem = lvPositions.Items.Add(SecToMin(TimeEnd))
//002283:                 Else
//002284:                     lvItem.Text = SecToMin(TimeEnd)
//002285:                 End If
//002286:             End While
//002287:         Catch ex As Exception
//002288:             MsgBox("Error reading the Comskip file", MsgBoxStyle.Exclamation, "Error reading the file")
//002289:         Finally
//002290:             sr.Close()
//002291:         End Try
//002292:         lvItem.SubItems.Add(SecToMin(MaxVal))
//002293: 
//002294:     End Sub
//002295:

//002346:     Private Sub mnuTestSeg_Click(ByVal sender As System.Object, ByVal e As System.EventArgs) Handles mnuTestSeg.Click
//002347:         TestSegment()
//002348:     End Sub
//002349: 
//002350:     Private Sub TestSegment()
//002351:         If lvPositions.Items.Count = 0 Then Exit Sub
//002352:         With lvPositions.SelectedItems
//002353:             If .Count = 0 Then Exit Sub
//002354:             ReDim mPlaySegments(.Count - 1)
//002355:             For i As Integer = 0 To .Count - 1
//002356:                 mPlaySegments(i) = New Segment
//002357:                 mPlaySegments(i).Start = MinToSec(.Item(i).Text)
//002358:                 mPlaySegments(i).Finish = MinToSec(.Item(i).SubItems(1).Text)
//002359:             Next
//002360:         End With
//002361:         PlaySelectedSegments()
//002362:     End Sub
//002363: 
//002364:     Private Sub Timer_Tick(ByVal sender As Object, _
//002365: ByVal e As System.EventArgs) Handles Timer.Tick
//002366: 
//002367:         If mIsAudio Then DrawWavePosition()
//002368:         If mPlaySelected Then
//002369:             If mPlayer.Ctlcontrols.currentPosition >= mPlaySegments(mPlaySelIndex).Finish Then
//002370:                 If UBound(mPlaySegments) > mPlaySelIndex Then
//002371:                     mPlaySelIndex += 1
//002372:                     mPlayer.Ctlcontrols.currentPosition = mPlaySegments(mPlaySelIndex).Start
//002373:                 Else
//002374:                     If mRepeatPlay Then
//002375:                         mPlaySelIndex = 0
//002376:                         mPlayer.Ctlcontrols.currentPosition = _
//002377:                             mPlaySegments(mPlaySelIndex).Start
//002378:                     Else
//002379:                         mPlayer.Ctlcontrols.stop()
//002380:                         mPlaySelected = False
//002381:                         Timer.Enabled = False
//002382:                     End If
//002383:                 End If
//002384:             End If
//002385:         End If
//002386: 
//002387:     End Sub

//002404:     End Sub

//002414:     Private Sub Mpcontrols_ButtonPress(ByVal Name As String) _
//002415:     Handles MPcontrols.ButtonPress
//002416: 
//002417:         Select Case Name
//002418:             Case "cStop"
//002419:                 mPlayer.Ctlcontrols.stop()
//002420:                 Timer.Enabled = False
//002421:             Case "cPlay"
//002422:                 If mPlayer.playState = WMPLib.WMPPlayState.wmppsPlaying Then
//002423:                     mPlayer.Ctlcontrols.pause()
//002424:                 Else
//002425:                     mPlayer.Ctlcontrols.play()
//002426:                 End If
//002427:                 mDisplayControl.Focus()
//002428:             Case "cBegin"
//002429:                 mPlayer.Ctlcontrols.currentPosition = 0
//002430:             Case "cFRev"
//002431:                 ToggleFastReverse()
//002432:             Case "cFFwd"
//002433:                 ToggleFastForward()
//002434:             Case "cEnd"
//002435:                 mPlayer.Ctlcontrols.pause()
//002436:                 mPlayer.Ctlcontrols.currentPosition = mPlayer.currentMedia.duration
//002437:             Case "cSelStrt"
//002438:                 StartSelection()
//002439:             Case "cSelEnd"
//002440:                 EndSelection()
//002441:             Case "cMute"
//002442:                 mPlayMuted = MPcontrols.Mute
//002443:         End Select
//002444: 
//002445:     End Sub
//002446:

//002465: 
//002466:     Private Sub frmMain_DragEnter(ByVal sender As Object, _
//002467:     ByVal e As System.Windows.Forms.DragEventArgs) _
//002468:     Handles MyBase.DragEnter
//002469: 
//002470:         If (e.Data.GetDataPresent(DataFormats.FileDrop)) Then
//002471:             e.Effect = DragDropEffects.Copy
//002472:         Else
//002473:             e.Effect = DragDropEffects.None
//002474:         End If
//002475: 
//002476:     End Sub
//002477: 
//002478:     Private Sub frmMain_DragDrop(ByVal sender As Object, _
//002479:     ByVal e As System.Windows.Forms.DragEventArgs) _
//002480:     Handles MyBase.DragDrop
//002481: 
//002482:         Dim arr As Array = DirectCast(e.Data.GetData(DataFormats.FileDrop), Array)
//002483:         Dim Filename As String
//002484: 
//002485:         If arr.GetLength(0) = 1 Then
//002486:             Filename = Convert.ToString(arr.GetValue(0))
//002487:             Try
//002488:                 If isValidExtension(Filename) Then
//002489:                     OpenFile(Filename)
//002490:                 End If
//002491:             Catch ex As Exception
//002492:                 MsgBox(ex.Message, MsgBoxStyle.Exclamation, "Invalid file format")
//002493:             End Try
//002494:         Else
//002495:             'TODO : Save the filelist to restore if no files are valid
//002496: 
//002497:             'Clear join list
//002498:             lvFiles.Items.Clear()
//002499:             Dim j As Integer, ValidFile As String
//002500:             For i As Integer = 0 To UBound(arr)
//002501:                 Filename = Convert.ToString(arr.GetValue(i))
//002502:                 Try
//002503:                     If isValidExtension(Filename) Then
//002504:                         lvFiles.Items.Add(Filename)
//002505:                         j += 1
//002506:                         ValidFile = Filename
//002507:                     End If
//002508:                 Catch ex As Exception
//002509:                     MsgBox(ex.Message, MsgBoxStyle.Exclamation, "Invalid file format")
//002510:                 End Try
//002511:             Next
//002512:             If j > 1 Then
//002513:                 mainTabs.SelectedTab = tabJoin
//002514:             ElseIf j = 1 Then
//002515:                 mMaskFile = False
//002516:                 OpenFile(ValidFile)
//002517:             Else
//002518:                 lvFiles.Items.Clear()
//002519:                 statMain.Text = mTranslator.LangText(49)
//002520:             End If
//002521:         End If
//002522: 
//002523:     End Sub
//002524: 
//002525:     Private Function isValidExtension(ByVal Filename As String, _
//002526:     Optional ByVal TestExt As String = ".mpg") As Boolean
//002527: 
//002528:         Dim fi As New FileInfo(Filename)
//002529:         Dim Ext As String = LCase(fi.Extension)
//002530: 
//002531:         If isValidExtenstionSlave(mStdToolMgr.ValidExtenstions(True), Ext) Then
//002532:             mMaskFile = (Ext = ".moviclip")
//002533:             Return True
//002534:         ElseIf isValidExtenstionSlave(".rm|.flv", Ext) Then
//002535:             Throw New ArgumentException("Configuration required for " + Filename + vbCrLf + _
//002536:             vbCrLf + "Files with extension '" + Ext + "' are supported but require external tools" + _
//002537:             vbCrLf + "See the Tools tab to learn more")
//002538:         Else
//002539:             Throw New ArgumentException("Error in reading file " + Filename + vbCrLf + _
//002540:             vbCrLf + "Files with extension '" + Ext + "' are not supported" + _
//002541:             vbCrLf + "Only .avi, .wmv, .asf, .mpg, .mpeg, .rm, .flv, .wma, .mp3 and .moviclip files are supported")
//002542:         End If
//002543: 
//002544:     End Function
//002545: 
//002546:     Private Function isValidExtenstionSlave(ByVal ExtStr As String, ByVal Ext As String) As Boolean
//002547:         Dim extArr As String() = Split(ExtStr, "|")
//002548:         For i As Integer = 0 To UBound(extArr)
//002549:             If Ext = extArr(i) Then Return True
//002550:         Next
//002551:     End Function
//002552: 
//002553: #End Region
//002554: 
//002555: #Region "   Keyboard shortcuts "
//002556: 
//002557:     Private Sub frmMain_KeyUp(ByVal sender As Object, _
//002558:     ByVal e As System.Windows.Forms.KeyEventArgs) Handles MyBase.KeyUp
//002559: 
//002560:         If Not mFileLoaded Then Exit Sub
//002561: 
//002562:         Select Case e.KeyCode
//002563: 
//002564:             Case Keys.Home     'Keys.Home
//002565:                 'Start selection
//002566:                 StartSelection()
//002567: 
//002568:             Case Keys.End     'Keys.End - end Selection
//002569:                 'End Selection
//002570:                 EndSelection()
//002571: 
//002572:             Case Keys.Delete    'Keys.Delete
//002573:                 If e.Control Then           'Control Delete
//002574:                     If lvPositions.Items.Count = 0 Then Exit Sub
//002575:                     lvPositions.Items.RemoveAt(lvPositions.Items.Count - 1)
//002576:                 End If
//002577: 
//002578:             Case Keys.Space     'Keys.Space
//002579:                 If mPlayer.playState <> 2 Then
//002580:                     mPlayer.Ctlcontrols.pause()
//002581:                 Else
//002582:                     mPlayer.Ctlcontrols.play()
//002583:                 End If
//002584:                 mDisplayControl.Focus()
//002585: 
//002586:             Case Keys.Left        'Left Arrow
//002587:                 If e.Control Then           'Control Left Arrow
//002588:                     mPlayer.Ctlcontrols.currentPosition -= 2
//002589:                 End If
//002590: 
//002591:             Case Keys.Right        'Right Arrow
//002592:                 If e.Control Then           'Control Right Arrow
//002593:                     mPlayer.Ctlcontrols.currentPosition += 2
//002594:                 End If
//002595: 
//002596:             Case Keys.Up        'Up Arrow
//002597:                 If e.Control Then
//002598:                     'Control+Up = Increase speed
//002599:                     ToggleFastForward()
//002600:                 ElseIf e.Alt Then
//002601:                     'change tuner resolution - coarser
//002602:                     If lvPositions.SelectedItems.Count = 1 Then
//002603:                         With FineResolution
//002604:                             Dim NewRes As Single = .Value
//002605:                             NewRes += CSng(0.01)
//002606:                             If NewRes <= .Maximum Then .Value = NewRes
//002607:                         End With
//002608:                     End If
//002609:                 Else
//002610:                     'Change volume
//002611:                     If mPlayer.playState = WMPLib.WMPPlayState.wmppsPlaying Then MPcontrols.IncreaseVolume()
//002612:                 End If
//002613: 
//002614:             Case Keys.Down       'Down Arrow
//002615:                 If e.Control Then
//002616:                     'Control+Down = Decrease speed
//002617:                     ToggleFastReverse()
//002618:                 ElseIf e.Alt Then
//002619:                     'change tuner resolution - finer
//002620:                     If lvPositions.SelectedItems.Count = 1 Then
//002621:                         With FineResolution
//002622:                             Dim NewRes As Single = .Value
//002623:                             NewRes -= CSng(0.01)
//002624:                             If NewRes >= .Minimum Then .Value = NewRes
//002625:                         End With
//002626:                     End If
//002627:                 Else
//002628:                     'Change volume
//002629:                     If mPlayer.playState = WMPLib.WMPPlayState.wmppsPlaying Then MPcontrols.DecreaseVolume()
//002630:                 End If
//002631: 
//002632:             Case Keys.Enter
//002633:                 If e.Alt Then
//002634:                     mPlayer.fullScreen = True
//002635:                 End If
//002636: 
//002637:         End Select
//002638: 
//002639:     End Sub
//002640: 
//002641:     Private Sub frmMain_KeyDown(ByVal sender As Object, ByVal e As System.Windows.Forms.KeyEventArgs) Handles MyBase.KeyDown
//002642: 
//002643:         If Not mFileLoaded Then Exit Sub
//002644: 
//002645:         Select Case e.KeyCode
//002646:             Case Keys.Left, Keys.Right
//002647:                 mSuspendPlayerRefresh = True
//002648:             Case Else
//002649:                 mSuspendPlayerRefresh = False
//002650:         End Select
//002651: 
//002652:     End Sub
//002653:

//002700:                 If mPlayer.URL = "" Then
//002701:                     lvPositions.Items.Clear()

//002704:

//002706:                 MPcontrols.SetToolbarMode(False)

//002712:     Private Sub mPlayer_KeyUpEvent(ByVal sender As System.Object, _
//002713:     ByVal e As AxWMPLib._WMPOCXEvents_KeyUpEvent) Handles mPlayer.KeyUpEvent
//002714: 
//002715:         If Not mFileLoaded Then Exit Sub
//002716: 
//002717:         Select Case e.nKeyCode
//002718: 
//002719:             Case 36     'Keys.Home
//002720:                 'Start selection
//002721:                 StartSelection()
//002722: 
//002723:             Case 35     'Keys.End - end Selection
//002724:                 'End Selection
//002725:                 EndSelection()
//002726: 
//002727:             Case 46     'Keys.Delete
//002728:                 If e.nShiftState = 2 Then           'Control Delete
//002729:                     If lvPositions.Items.Count = 0 Then Exit Sub
//002730:                     lvPositions.Items.RemoveAt(lvPositions.Items.Count - 1)
//002731:                 End If
//002732: 
//002733:             Case 32     'Keys.Space
//002734:                 If mPlayer.playState <> 2 Then
//002735:                     mPlayer.Ctlcontrols.pause()
//002736:                 Else
//002737:                     mPlayer.Ctlcontrols.play()
//002738:                 End If
//002739: 
//002740:             Case 37         'Left Arrow
//002741:                 If e.nShiftState = 2 Then           'Control Left Arrow
//002742:                     mPlayer.Ctlcontrols.currentPosition -= 2
//002743:                 End If
//002744: 
//002745:             Case 39         'Right Arrow
//002746:                 If e.nShiftState = 2 Then           'Control Right Arrow
//002747:                     mPlayer.Ctlcontrols.currentPosition += 2
//002748:                 End If
//002749: 
//002750:             Case 38         'Up Arrow
//002751:                 If e.nShiftState = 2 Then
//002752:                     'Control+Up = Increase speed
//002753:                     ToggleFastForward()
//002754:                 Else
//002755:                     'Change volume
//002756:                     If mPlayer.playState = WMPLib.WMPPlayState.wmppsPlaying Then MPcontrols.IncreaseVolume()
//002757:                 End If
//002758: 
//002759:             Case 40         'Down Arrow
//002760:                 If e.nShiftState = 2 Then
//002761:                     'Control+Down = Decrease speed
//002762:                     ToggleFastReverse()
//002763:                 Else
//002764:                     'Change volume
//002765:                     If mPlayer.playState = WMPLib.WMPPlayState.wmppsPlaying Then MPcontrols.DecreaseVolume()
//002766:                 End If
//002767: 
//002768:         End Select
//002769:     End Sub
//002770: 
//002771:     Private Sub mPlayer_PlayStateChange(ByVal sender As Object, _
//002772:     ByVal e As AxWMPLib._WMPOCXEvents_PlayStateChangeEvent) _
//002773:     Handles mPlayer.PlayStateChange
//002774: 
//002775:         With mPlayer
//002776:             Select Case .playState
//002777:                 Case WMPLib.WMPPlayState.wmppsStopped
//002778:                     'Stop fast play when stopped
//002779:                     ' Don't bother when player is paused
//002780:                     mFFwd = False
//002781:                     mFRev = False
//002782:                     .settings.rate = 1
//002783:                     FinishTheList()
//002784:                     lvPositions.Select()
//002785: 
//002786:                     mPlaySelected = False       'Restore player to ordinary control
//002787:                     Timer.Enabled = False       'Disable timer
//002788:                     Me.TopMost = False          'Form is not top most
//002789:                 Case WMPLib.WMPPlayState.wmppsPlaying
//002790:                     If chkOnTop.Checked Then
//002791:                         Me.TopMost = True
//002792:                     Else
//002793:                         Me.TopMost = False
//002794:                     End If
//002795:                 Case Else
//002796:                     Me.TopMost = False
//002797:             End Select
//002798:         End With
//002799: 
//002800:     End Sub
//002801:

//002842:                 DisplayFineControls(False)
//002843:             Case 4
//002844:                 panSegments.Width = 0
//002845:                 DisplayFineControls(False)
//002846:             Case 5
//002847:                 panSegments.Width = 0
//002848:                 DisplayFineControls(False)

//002856: 
//002857:     Private Sub ToolBar1_ButtonClick(ByVal sender As System.Object, ByVal e As System.Windows.Forms.ToolBarButtonClickEventArgs) Handles tbJoin.ButtonClick
//002858: 
//002859:         Select Case DirectCast(e.Button.Tag, String)
//002860:             Case "Open"
//002861:                 OpenFilesForJoining()
//002862: 
//002863:             Case "Join"
//002864:                 If lvFiles.Items.Count = 0 Then Exit Sub
//002865: 
//002866:                 Dim fi As New FileInfo(lvFiles.Items(0).Text)
//002867:                 mInFile = fi.FullName
//002868:                 If Not CreateHandler(fi.Extension) Then Exit Sub
//002869:                 mPlayer.URL = ""
//002870: 
//002871:                 UpdateHandlerOptions()
//002872: 
//002873:                 dlgSaveFile.InitialDirectory = dlgOpenFile.InitialDirectory
//002874:                 dlgSaveFile.DefaultExt = mHandler.Extension
//002875:                 dlgSaveFile.FileName = ""
//002876:                 dlgSaveFile.Filter = mHandler.Extension(True) + " |*" + mHandler.Extension
//002877: 
//002878:                 If dlgSaveFile.ShowDialog() = Windows.Forms.DialogResult.OK Then
//002879:                     Me.Refresh()
//002880:                     Dim Filename As String = dlgSaveFile.FileName
//002881: 
//002882:                     Dim Temp As String()
//002883:                     With lvFiles
//002884:                         ReDim Temp(.Items.Count - 1)
//002885:                         For i As Integer = 0 To .Items.Count - 1
//002886:                             Temp(i) = .Items(i).Text
//002887:                         Next
//002888: 
//002889:                         statMain.Text = Replace(mTranslator.LangText(38), "{%1}", CStr(.Items.Count))
//002890:                         'statMain.Text = "Joining " + CStr(.Items.Count) + " files. Please wait..."
//002891: 
//002892:                         mainTabs.SelectedTab = tabTrace
//002893:                         rtfTrace.SelectedText = vbCrLf
//002894: 
//002895:                         If chkKeepMRU.Checked Then rtfTrace.Clear()
//002896: 
//002897:                         If mHandler.Join(Temp, Filename) Then
//002898:                             UpdateRTF(vbCrLf & "Success!!" & vbCrLf, _
//002899:                                 modMain.MessageType.Success)
//002900:                             ShowProcessStat(modMain.MessageType.Success)
//002901:                             If chkDel.Checked Then
//002902:                                 'Send all the files to the recycle bin
//002903:                                 For i As Integer = 0 To lvFiles.Items.Count - 1
//002904:                                     TrashFile(Temp(i))
//002905:                                 Next
//002906:                             End If
//002907:                         Else
//002908:                             UpdateRTF(vbCrLf + "Joining Failed !!" & vbCrLf, _
//002909:                                 modMain.MessageType.Failure)
//002910:                             ShowProcessStat(modMain.MessageType.Failure)
//002911:                         End If
//002912:                     End With
//002913:                     statMain.Text = mTranslator.LangText(23)
//002914:                     If chkBeep.Checked Then Beep()
//002915:                 End If
//002916: 
//002917:             Case "Remove"
//002918:                 If lvFiles.Items.Count = 0 Then Exit Sub
//002919:                 'Dim DoomedItems As ListView.SelectedListViewItemCollection
//002920:                 'DoomedItems = lvFiles.SelectedItems
//002921:                 For Each Item As ListViewItem In lvFiles.SelectedItems
//002922:                     lvFiles.Items.Remove(Item)
//002923:                 Next
//002924: 
//002925:             Case "Sort"
//002926:                 Dim TempIn As String()
//002927:                 With lvFiles
//002928:                     ReDim TempIn(.Items.Count - 1)
//002929:                     For i As Integer = 0 To .Items.Count - 1
//002930:                         TempIn(i) = .Items(i).Text
//002931:                     Next
//002932:                     Array.Sort(TempIn)
//002933:                     .Items.Clear()
//002934:                     For i As Integer = 0 To UBound(TempIn)
//002935:                         .Items.Add(TempIn(i))
//002936:                     Next
//002937:                 End With
//002938: 
//002939:             Case "Clear"
//002940:                 lvFiles.Items.Clear()
//002941: 
//002942:             Case "Up"
//002943:                 'Move files up
//002944:                 If lvFiles.Items.Count = 0 Then Exit Sub
//002945:                 If lvFiles.SelectedItems.Count = 0 Then Exit Sub
//002946:                 MoveItemsUp(lvFiles)
//002947: 
//002948:             Case "Dn"
//002949:                 'Move files down
//002950:                 If lvFiles.Items.Count = 0 Then Exit Sub
//002951:                 If lvFiles.SelectedItems.Count = 0 Then Exit Sub
//002952:                 MoveItemsDn(lvFiles)
//002953: 
//002954:             Case "Info"
//002955:                 With lvFiles
//002956:                     If .Items.Count = 0 Then Exit Sub
//002957:                     Dim fi As New FileInfo(lvFiles.Items(0).Text)
//002958:                     If Not CreateHandler(fi.Extension) Then Exit Sub
//002959:                     mainTabs.SelectedTab = tabTrace
//002960:                     mHandler.ShowInfo(GetSelectedFilenames)
//002961:                 End With
//002962:         End Select
//002963: 
//002964:     End Sub
//002965: 
//002966:     Private Sub UpdateToolbar(ByVal Enable As Boolean)
//002967:         If Enable Then
//002968:             cSort.Enabled = True
//002969:             cRemove.Enabled = True
//002970:             cClear.Enabled = True
//002971:             cJoin.Enabled = True
//002972:             cUp.Enabled = True
//002973:             cDn.Enabled = True
//002974:             cInfo.Enabled = True
//002975:         Else
//002976:             cSort.Enabled = False
//002977:             cRemove.Enabled = False
//002978:             cClear.Enabled = False
//002979:             cJoin.Enabled = False
//002980:             cUp.Enabled = False
//002981:             cDn.Enabled = False
//002982:             cInfo.Enabled = False
//002983:         End If
//002984:     End Sub
//002985: 
//002986:     Private Sub OpenFilesForJoining()
//002987: 
//002988:         With dlgOpenFile
//002989:             Dim Filter As String = mStdToolMgr.ValidExtenstions(True)
//002990:             Filter = Replace(Filter, ".", "*.")
//002991:             Filter = Replace(Filter, "|", ";")
//002992: 
//002993:             .Filter = "Supported Media Files|" & Filter
//002994:             .Multiselect = True
//002995:             If chkDialogView.Checked Then mOpenFileExtender.Enabled = True
//002996: 
//002997:             If .ShowDialog() = Windows.Forms.DialogResult.OK Then
//002998:                 If Len(.FileName) > 0 Then
//002999:                     'Rajat check for compatible extensions and file exists
//003000:                     If .FileNames.Length > 1 Then
//003001:                         For i As Integer = 0 To .FileNames.GetUpperBound(0)
//003002:                             If File.Exists(.FileNames(i)) Then
//003003:                                 lvFiles.Items.Add(.FileNames(i))
//003004:                             End If
//003005:                         Next
//003006:                     Else
//003007:                         If File.Exists(.FileName) Then
//003008:                             lvFiles.Items.Add(.FileName)
//003009:                             If chkAuto.Checked Then
//003010:                                 Dim Matches As String() = FindLikeFiles(.FileName)
//003011:                                 If Not Matches Is Nothing Then
//003012:                                     For i As Integer = 0 To UBound(Matches)
//003013:                                         lvFiles.Items.Add(Matches(i))
//003014:                                     Next
//003015:                                 End If
//003016:                             End If
//003017:                         End If
//003018:                     End If
//003019:                 End If
//003020:             End If
//003021:             mOpenFileExtender.Enabled = False
//003022:         End With
//003023: 
//003024:     End Sub
//003025: 
//003026:     Private Function GetSelectedFilenames() As String()
//003027:         Dim Temp As String()
//003028:         With lvFiles
//003029:             If .SelectedItems.Count = 0 Then
//003030:                 ReDim Temp(.Items.Count - 1)
//003031:                 For i As Integer = 0 To UBound(Temp)
//003032:                     Temp(i) = .Items(i).Text
//003033:                 Next
//003034:             Else
//003035:                 ReDim Temp(.SelectedItems.Count - 1)
//003036:                 For i As Integer = 0 To UBound(Temp)
//003037:                     Temp(i) = .SelectedItems(i).Text
//003038:                 Next
//003039:             End If
//003040:         End With
//003041:         Return Temp
//003042:     End Function
//003043: 
//003044:     Private Function FindLikeFiles(ByVal Filename As String) As String()
//003045: 
//003046:         Dim Temp As String()
//003047:         Dim fi As New FileInfo(Filename)
//003048:         Dim di As DirectoryInfo = fi.Directory
//003049: 
//003050:         Dim Template As String = fi.Name
//003051:         Template = Template.Remove(Template.Length - fi.Extension.Length, _
//003052:             fi.Extension.Length)
//003053: 
//003054:         Dim Started As Boolean, CharVal As Integer
//003055:         For i As Integer = Template.Length - 1 To 0 Step -1
//003056:             CharVal = Asc(Template.Chars(i))
//003057:             If (CharVal < 58) AndAlso (CharVal > 47) Then
//003058:                 Started = True
//003059:             End If
//003060:             If Started Then
//003061:                 If (CharVal > 57) Or (CharVal < 48) Then
//003062:                     Template = Template.Remove(i, Template.Length - i)
//003063:                     Exit For
//003064:                 End If
//003065:             End If
//003066:         Next
//003067: 
//003068:         Dim mfi As FileInfo, mfis As FileInfo()
//003069:         mfis = di.GetFiles(Template + "*")
//003070:         Dim MediaGrp As MediaTypes.Format = mTypes.FindFormat(fi.Extension)
//003071: 
//003072:         Dim j As Integer
//003073:         If mfis.Length > 1 Then
//003074:             ReDim Temp(mfis.Length - 2)
//003075:             For Each mfi In mfis
//003076:                 If mfi.FullName <> Filename Then
//003077:                     If mTypes.ExtSupported(MediaGrp, mfi.Extension) Then
//003078:                         Temp(j) = mfi.FullName
//003079:                         j += 1
//003080:                     End If
//003081:                 End If
//003082:             Next
//003083:         End If
//003084: 
//003085:         If j > 0 Then ReDim Preserve Temp(j - 1)
//003086: 
//003087:         Return Temp
//003088: 
//003089:     End Function
//003090: 
//003091: #End Region
//003092: 
//003093: #Region "   Positions List "
//003094: 
//003095:     Private Sub lvPositions_KeyDown(ByVal sender As System.Object, _
//003096:     ByVal e As System.Windows.Forms.KeyEventArgs) _
//003097:     Handles lvPositions.KeyDown, lvFiles.KeyUp
//003098: 
//003099:         Dim lvControl As ListView
//003100:         lvControl = DirectCast(sender, ListView)
//003101: 
//003102:         With lvControl
//003103:             If .Items.Count = 0 Then Exit Sub
//003104:             If .SelectedItems.Count = 0 Then Exit Sub
//003105: 
//003106:             mAllowListIndexChange = True
//003107: 
//003108:             Select Case e.KeyCode
//003109:                 Case Keys.Delete
//003110:                     DeleteSelected()
//003111: 
//003112:                 Case Keys.F11
//003113:                     'move up
//003114:                     MoveItemsUp(lvControl)
//003115: 
//003116:                 Case Keys.F12
//003117:                     'move down
//003118:                     MoveItemsDn(lvControl)
//003119: 
//003120:                 Case Keys.C
//003121:                     'Copy
//003122:                     If e.Control Then
//003123:                         CopySelected()
//003124:                     End If
//003125: 
//003126:                 Case Keys.V
//003127:                     'Paste
//003128:                     If e.Control Then
//003129:                         PasteSelected()
//003130:                     End If
//003131: 
//003132:                 Case Keys.Left
//003133:                     'Need to jump around the bug with index change
//003134:                     'Doing this instead of keeping last index to avoid problems with delete
//003135:                     If e.Control Then Exit Sub
//003136:                     mAllowListIndexChange = False
//003137: 
//003138:                     If e.Shift Then         'Shift means right slider
//003139:                         DoFrameAdjustment(False, False)
//003140:                     Else
//003141:                         DoFrameAdjustment(True, False)
//003142:                     End If
//003143: 
//003144:                 Case Keys.Right
//003145:                     'Need to jump around the bug with index change
//003146:                     'Doing this instead of keeping last index to avoid problems with delete
//003147:                     If e.Control Then Exit Sub
//003148:                     mAllowListIndexChange = False
//003149: 
//003150:                     If e.Shift Then         'Shift means right slider
//003151:                         DoFrameAdjustment(False, True)
//003152:                     Else
//003153:                         DoFrameAdjustment(True, True)
//003154:                         'Debug.WriteLine(GetAsyncKeyState(39))
//003155:                     End If
//003156: 
//003157:             End Select
//003158:         End With
//003159: 
//003160:     End Sub
//003161: 
//003162:     Private Sub DoFrameAdjustment(ByVal ChangeStart As Boolean, _
//003163: ByVal Forward As Boolean)
//003164: 
//003165:         If lvPositions.SelectedItems.Count <> 1 Then Exit Sub
//003166: 
//003167:         Dim StepValue As Integer, Position, NewPosition As Double
//003168: 
//003169:         If Forward Then
//003170:             StepValue = 1
//003171:         Else
//003172:             StepValue = -1
//003173:         End If
//003174: 
//003175:         lvSelectionInit()
//003176: 
//003177:         If ChangeStart Then
//003178:             Position = mSelStrt
//003179:         Else
//003180:             If mOneSidedSelection Then Exit Sub
//003181:             Position = mSelStop
//003182:         End If
//003183: 
//003184:         mPlayer.Ctlcontrols.currentPosition = Position
//003185:         NewPosition = Position + StepValue * FineResolution.Value
//003186: 
//003187:         With lvPositions.SelectedItems(0)
//003188:             If ChangeStart Then
//003189:                 If NewPosition >= mSelStop Then Exit Sub
//003190:                 .SubItems(0).Text = SecToMin(Math.Round(NewPosition, 3))
//003191:             Else
//003192:                 If NewPosition <= MinToSec(.SubItems(0).Text) Then Exit Sub
//003193:                 If NewPosition >= mPlayer.currentMedia.duration Then Exit Sub
//003194:                 .SubItems(1).Text = SecToMin(Math.Round(NewPosition, 3))
//003195:             End If
//003196:         End With
//003197: 
//003198:         mPlayer.Ctlcontrols.currentPosition = NewPosition
//003199:         mSelsDirty = True
//003200:         UpdateSelDur()
//003201: 
//003202:     End Sub
//003203: 
//003204:     'To accomodate the fast adjustment of video
//003205:     Private Sub lvPositions_KeyUp(ByVal sender As Object, ByVal e As System.Windows.Forms.KeyEventArgs) _
//003206:     Handles lvPositions.KeyUp
//003207: 
//003208:         If lvPositions.SelectedItems.Count <> 1 Then Exit Sub
//003209:         If e.KeyCode = Keys.Space Then
//003210:             TestSegment()
//003211:         Else
//003212:             MPcontrols.RefreshPositions()
//003213:         End If
//003214: 
//003215:     End Sub
//003216: 
//003217:     Private Sub MoveItemsUp(ByVal lvControl As ListView)
//003218: 
//003219:         With lvControl
//003220:             Dim NumSelected As Integer = .SelectedIndices.Count
//003221:             If .SelectedIndices.Contains(0) Then Exit Sub
//003222: 
//003223:             Dim Jump2 As Integer = .SelectedIndices.Item(NumSelected - 1) + 1
//003224: 
//003225:             For i As Integer = .SelectedIndices.Count - 1 To 0 Step -1
//003226:                 If i > 0 Then
//003227:                     'There is another selected item
//003228:                     If .SelectedIndices.Item(i - 1) = .SelectedIndices.Item(i) - 1 Then
//003229:                         'Contiguous item; check next item
//003230:                     Else
//003231:                         JumpItem(lvControl, .Items(.SelectedIndices.Item(i) - 1), Jump2)
//003232:                         Jump2 = .SelectedIndices.Item(i - 1) + 1
//003233:                     End If
//003234:                 Else
//003235:                     'This is the last selected item
//003236:                     JumpItem(lvControl, .Items(.SelectedIndices.Item(i) - 1), Jump2)
//003237:                 End If
//003238:             Next
//003239:         End With
//003240:         mSelsDirty = True
//003241: 
//003242:     End Sub
//003243: 
//003244:     Private Sub MoveItemsDn(ByVal lvControl As ListView)
//003245:         With lvControl
//003246:             Dim NumSelected As Integer = .SelectedIndices.Count
//003247:             If .SelectedIndices.Contains(.Items.Count - 1) Then Exit Sub
//003248: 
//003249:             Dim Jump2 As Integer = .SelectedIndices.Item(0)
//003250:             For i As Integer = 0 To .SelectedIndices.Count - 1
//003251:                 If i < NumSelected - 1 Then
//003252:                     'There is another selected item
//003253:                     If .SelectedIndices.Item(i + 1) = .SelectedIndices.Item(i) + 1 Then
//003254:                         'Contiguous item; check next item
//003255:                     Else
//003256:                         JumpItem(lvControl, .Items(.SelectedIndices.Item(i) + 1), Jump2)
//003257:                         Jump2 = .SelectedIndices.Item(i + 1)
//003258:                     End If
//003259:                 Else
//003260:                     'This is the last selected item
//003261:                     JumpItem(lvControl, .Items(.SelectedIndices.Item(i) + 1), Jump2)
//003262:                 End If
//003263:             Next
//003264:         End With
//003265:         mSelsDirty = True
//003266: 
//003267:     End Sub
//003268: 
//003269:     Private Sub lvPositions_SelectedIndexChanged(ByVal sender As Object, _
//003270: ByVal e As System.EventArgs) Handles lvPositions.SelectedIndexChanged
//003271: 
//003272:         If Not mAllowListIndexChange Then Exit Sub
//003273: 
//003274:         If lvPositions.SelectedItems.Count = 1 Then
//003275:             lvSelectionInit()
//003276:             mPlayer.Ctlcontrols.currentPosition = mSelStrt
//003277:             mPlayer.Ctlcontrols.pause()
//003278:             MPcontrols.RefreshPositions()
//003279:         Else
//003280:             DisplayFineControls(False)
//003281:         End If
//003282:         Timer.Enabled = False
//003283: 
//003284:     End Sub
//003285: 
//003286:     Private Sub lvSelectionInit()
//003287: 
//003288:         With lvPositions.SelectedItems(0)
//003289:             mSelStrt = MinToSec(.Text)
//003290:             If .SubItems.Count = 1 Then
//003291:                 mSelStop = mPlayer.currentMedia.duration
//003292:                 mOneSidedSelection = True
//003293:             Else
//003294:                 mSelStop = MinToSec(.SubItems(1).Text)
//003295:                 mOneSidedSelection = False
//003296:             End If
//003297:         End With
//003298: 
//003299:         DisplayFineControls(True)
//003300: 
//003301:     End Sub
//003302: 
//003303:     Private Sub lvPositions_GotFocus(ByVal sender As Object, _
//003304:     ByVal e As System.EventArgs) Handles lvPositions.GotFocus, lvFiles.GotFocus
//003305: 
//003306:         Dim ListView As ListView = DirectCast(sender, ListView)
//003307:         If ListView.Items.Count = 0 Then Exit Sub
//003308:         If ListView.SelectedIndices.Count = 0 Then
//003309:             ListView.Items(0).Selected = True
//003310:         End If
//003311: 
//003312:     End Sub

//003324:             MenuItem9.Enabled = True
//003325:             MenuItem10.Enabled = True
//003326:         End If

//003346:     Private Sub DeleteSelected()
//003347:         With lvPositions
//003348:             Dim Segment As ListViewItem
//003349:             For Each Segment In .SelectedItems
//003350:                 .Items.Remove(Segment)
//003351:             Next
//003352:         End With
//003353:         UpdateSelDur()
//003354:         mSelsDirty = True
//003355:     End Sub
//003356: 
//003357:     Private Sub CopySelected()
//003358:         With lvPositions
//003359:             ReDim mItems(.SelectedItems.Count - 1)
//003360:             For i As Integer = 0 To .SelectedItems.Count - 1
//003361:                 mItems(i) = .SelectedItems(i)
//003362:             Next
//003363:         End With
//003364:     End Sub
//003365: 
//003366:     Private Sub PasteSelected()
//003367:         If mItems(0) Is Nothing Then Exit Sub
//003368:         Dim CopyTo As Integer, TempItem As ListViewItem
//003369: 
//003370:         With lvPositions
//003371:             If .SelectedItems.Count = 0 Then
//003372:                 CopyTo = .Items.Count - 1
//003373:             Else
//003374:                 CopyTo = .SelectedItems(0).Index
//003375:             End If
//003376:             For i As Integer = 1 To mItems.Length
//003377:                 TempItem = DirectCast(mItems(i - 1).Clone, ListViewItem)
//003378:                 .Items.Insert(CopyTo + i, TempItem)
//003379:             Next
//003380:         End With
//003381:         UpdateSelDur()
//003382:         mSelsDirty = True
//003383:     End Sub
//003384:

//003418:     Private Function Safe2ShowTuner() As Boolean
//003419: 
//003420:         Select Case lvPositions.SelectedItems.Count
//003421:             Case 0, Is > 1
//003422:                 Return False
//003423:             Case 1
//003424:                 If lvPositions.SelectedItems(0).SubItems.Count = 1 Then Return False
//003425:         End Select
//003426:         Return True
//003427: 
//003428:     End Function

//003431: 
//003432: #Region "   Utility and Worker Functions "
//003433: 
//003434:     Private Sub JumpItem(ByVal lvControl As ListView, _
//003435:         ByVal Item As ListViewItem, ByVal Jump2Pos As Integer)
//003436: 
//003437:         With lvControl
//003438:             Dim TempItem As ListViewItem = DirectCast(Item.Clone, ListViewItem)
//003439:             .Items.Insert(Jump2Pos, TempItem)
//003440:             .Items.Remove(Item)
//003441:         End With
//003442: 
//003443:     End Sub
//003444: 
//003445:     Private Function CreateHandler(ByVal Extension As String) As Boolean
//003446: 
//003447:         Timer.Enabled = False
//003448:         Try
//003449:             'Create a handler instance based on extension
//003450:             Select Case LCase(Extension)
//003451:                 Case ".mpg", ".mpeg"
//003452:                     mHandler = New MPGhandler(Me, mInFile)
//003453:                     mIsAudio = False
//003454:                 Case ".wmv", ".asf"
//003455:                     mHandler = New ASFhandler(Me, mInFile)
//003456:                     mIsAudio = False
//003457:                 Case ".avi"
//003458:                     mHandler = New AVIhandler(Me, mInFile)
//003459:                     mIsAudio = False
//003460:                 Case ".rm"
//003461:                     mHandler = New RMhandler(Me, mInFile)
//003462:                     mIsAudio = False
//003463:                 Case ".flv"
//003464:                     mHandler = New FLVhandler(Me, mInFile)
//003465:                     mIsAudio = False
//003466:                 Case ".mp3"
//003467:                     mHandler = New MPGhandler(Me, mInFile, True)
//003468:                     mIsAudio = True
//003469:                 Case ".wma"
//003470:                     mHandler = New ASFhandler(Me, mInFile, True)
//003471:                     mIsAudio = True
//003472:                 Case Else
//003473:                     MsgBox("Filetype not supported: " + Extension)
//003474:                     mPlayer.URL = ""
//003475:                     mHandler = Nothing
//003476:                     SwitchVisual(True)
//003477:                     Return False
//003478:             End Select
//003479:         Catch ex As Exception
//003480:             MsgBox(ex.Message)
//003481:         End Try
//003482: 
//003483:         SwitchVisual(False)
//003484:         Return True
//003485: 
//003486:     End Function
//003487: 
//003488:     Private Function SecToMin(ByVal Sec As Double) As String
//003489: 
//003490:         Dim TempDt As Date
//003491:         TempDt = Date.FromOADate(Sec / 86400)    '24 * 60 * 60
//003492:         If Sec >= 3600 Then
//003493:             Return TempDt.ToString("HH:mm:ss.fff")
//003494:         Else
//003495:             Return TempDt.ToString("mm:ss.fff")
//003496:         End If
//003497: 
//003498:     End Function
//003499: 
//003500:     Private Function MinToSec(ByVal Min As String) As Double
//003501: 
//003502:         Dim Temp As String()
//003503: 
//003504:         Temp = Split(Min, ":")
//003505: 
//003506:         Select Case UBound(Temp)
//003507:             Case 0
//003508:                 Return Val(Temp(0))
//003509:             Case 1
//003510:                 Return (Val(Temp(0)) * 60) + Val(Temp(1))
//003511:             Case 2
//003512:                 Return (Val(Temp(0)) * 3600) + (Val(Temp(1)) * 60) + Val(Temp(2))
//003513:         End Select
//003514: 
//003515:     End Function
//003516: 
//003517:     Private Function TrashFile(ByRef sPath As String) As Boolean
//003518:         Dim FileOp As SHFILEOPSTRUCT
//003519:         If Not File.Exists(sPath) Then
//003520:             MsgBox("Could not find " & sPath & "." & vbCrLf _
//003521:             & "Please verify the path.")
//003522:             Return True
//003523:         End If
//003524:         With FileOp
//003525:             .wFunc = FO_DELETE
//003526:             .pFrom = sPath & vbNullChar
//003527:             .pTo = vbNullChar
//003528:             .fFlags = FOF_NOCONFIRMATION Or FOF_ALLOWUNDO
//003529:             .lpszProgressTitle = "Sending " & sPath & " to the Recycle Bin"
//003530:         End With
//003531:         Try
//003532:             SHFileOperation(FileOp)
//003533:         Catch ex As Exception
//003534:             MsgBox(ex.Message)
//003535:         End Try
//003536:     End Function
//003537: 
//003538:     Private Sub ToggleFastForward()
//003539: 
//003540:         'Pause the player and reset other buttons
//003541:         mPlayer.Ctlcontrols.pause()
//003542:         mFRev = False
//003543:         MPcontrols.cFRev.Pushed = False
//003544: 
//003545:         'Start it again
//003546:         If mFFwd Then
//003547:             mFFwd = False
//003548:             mPlayer.settings.rate = 1
//003549:         Else
//003550:             mFFwd = True
//003551:             mPlayer.settings.rate = 2
//003552:         End If
//003553:         mPlayer.Ctlcontrols.play()
//003554:         MPcontrols.cFFwd.Pushed = mFFwd
//003555: 
//003556:     End Sub
//003557: 
//003558:     Private Sub ToggleFastReverse()
//003559: 
//003560:         'Pause the player and reset other buttons
//003561:         mPlayer.Ctlcontrols.pause()
//003562:         mFFwd = False
//003563:         MPcontrols.cFFwd.Pushed = False
//003564: 
//003565:         'Start it again
//003566:         mPlayer.Ctlcontrols.pause()
//003567:         If mFRev Then
//003568:             mFRev = False
//003569:             mPlayer.settings.rate = 1
//003570:         Else
//003571:             mFRev = True
//003572:             mPlayer.settings.rate = -2
//003573:         End If
//003574:         mPlayer.Ctlcontrols.play()
//003575:         MPcontrols.cFRev.Pushed = mFRev
//003576: 
//003577:     End Sub
//003578: 
//003579:     Private Sub ResetFastButtons()
//003580:         mFFwd = False
//003581:         mFRev = False
//003582:         MPcontrols.cFFwd.Pushed = False
//003583:         MPcontrols.cFRev.Pushed = False
//003584:     End Sub
//003585: 
//003586:     Private Sub StartSelection()
//003587: 
//003588:         Dim CurrPos As Double
//003589:         CurrPos = Math.Round(mPlayer.Ctlcontrols.currentPosition, 3)
//003590: 
//003591:         'Debug.Write(CurrPos)
//003592:         'Debug.WriteLine(Timer.Enabled)
//003593: 
//003594:         Dim Last As Integer = lvPositions.Items.Count - 1
//003595: 
//003596:         With lvPositions
//003597:             If Last < 0 Then
//003598:                 'Create new item; because first entry
//003599:                 Dim NewItem As New ListViewItem
//003600:                 If CurrPos < mReactTime Then
//003601:                     NewItem.Text = "0"
//003602:                 Else
//003603:                     NewItem.Text = SecToMin(CurrPos - mReactTime)
//003604:                 End If
//003605:                 lvPositions.Items.Add(NewItem)
//003606:             ElseIf .Items(Last).SubItems.Count > 1 Then
//003607:                 'Create new item; because end exists
//003608:                 Dim NewItem As New ListViewItem
//003609:                 If CurrPos < mReactTime Then
//003610:                     NewItem.Text = "0"
//003611:                 Else
//003612:                     NewItem.Text = SecToMin(CurrPos - mReactTime)
//003613:                 End If
//003614:                 lvPositions.Items.Add(NewItem)
//003615:             Else
//003616:                 'Change start
//003617:                 If CurrPos < mReactTime Then
//003618:                     .Items(Last).Text = "0"
//003619:                 Else
//003620:                     .Items(Last).Text = SecToMin(CurrPos - mReactTime)
//003621:                 End If
//003622:             End If
//003623:         End With
//003624:         mSelsDirty = True
//003625: 
//003626:     End Sub
//003627: 
//003628:     Private Sub EndSelection()
//003629: 
//003630:         Dim CurrPos As Double
//003631:         CurrPos = Math.Round(mPlayer.Ctlcontrols.currentPosition, 3)
//003632: 
//003633:         'Debug.Write(CurrPos)
//003634:         'Debug.WriteLine(Timer.Enabled)
//003635: 
//003636:         Dim Last As Integer = lvPositions.Items.Count - 1
//003637:         If Last < 0 Then Exit Sub
//003638: 
//003639:         With lvPositions.Items(Last)
//003640:             If CurrPos - mReactTime <= MinToSec(.Text) Then Exit Sub
//003641:             If .SubItems.Count = 1 Then
//003642:                 'Add End
//003643:                 .SubItems.Add(SecToMin(CurrPos - mReactTime))
//003644:             Else
//003645:                 'Change End
//003646:                 .SubItems(1).Text = SecToMin(CurrPos - mReactTime)
//003647:             End If
//003648:         End With
//003649: 
//003650:         UpdateSelDur()
//003651:         mSelsDirty = True
//003652: 
//003653:     End Sub
//003654: 
//003655:     Private Sub UpdateSelDur()
//003656:         If lvPositions.Items.Count = 0 Then Exit Sub
//003657:         Dim Sel As Double
//003658:         With lvPositions
//003659:             For i As Integer = 0 To .Items.Count - 1
//003660:                 If .Items(i).SubItems.Count = 1 Then Exit For
//003661:                 Sel += MinToSec(.Items(i).SubItems(1).Text) - MinToSec(.Items(i).Text)
//003662:             Next
//003663:         End With
//003664: 
//003665:         statSel.Text = mTranslator.LangText(120) & ":" & mHandler.CFmt(Sel, True) 'Math.Round(Sel, 3).ToString
//003666:     End Sub
//003667: 
//003668:     Private Sub UpdateHandlerOptions()
//003669:         If mHandler Is Nothing Then Exit Sub
//003670:         mHandler.Options("FrameAccurate") = CStr(chkFrameAccurate.Checked)
//003671:         mHandler.Options("ForceJoin") = CStr(chkForceJoin.Checked)
//003672:     End Sub

//003674:     Private Function StripExtention(ByVal Filename As String) As String

//003689:

//003704:         mnuSaveX.Enabled = EditingSupported

//003706:         mnuInfo.Enabled = EditingSupported

//003709: 
//003710:         Select Case LCase(Extension)
//003711:             Case ".wmv", ".asf"
//003712:                 mnuImpSkip.Enabled = CheckForSkipFile("SmartSkip")
//003713:                 mnuImpComskip.Enabled = False
//003714:             Case ".mpg", ".mpeg"
//003715:                 mnuImpSkip.Enabled = CheckForSkipFile("SmartSkip")
//003716:                 mnuImpComskip.Enabled = CheckForSkipFile("Comskip")
//003717:             Case Else
//003718:                 mnuImpSkip.Enabled = False
//003719:                 mnuImpComskip.Enabled = False
//003720:         End Select
//003721:     End Sub
//003722: 
//003723:     Private Function CheckForSkipFile(ByVal Type As String) As Boolean
//003724: 
//003725:         Dim SkipFilename As String
//003726:         Select Case Type
//003727:             Case "Comskip"
//003728:                 SkipFilename = StripExtention(mInFile) & ".txt"

//003730:                 SkipFilename = mInFile & ".chapters.xml"

//003734:             Dim fi As New FileInfo(SkipFilename)
//003735:             Return fi.Exists
//003736:         Catch ex As Exception
//003737:             'do nothing
//003738:         End Try
//003739: 
//003740:     End Function
//003741: 
//003742:     Private Sub cSplit_Click(ByVal sender As System.Object, _
//003743:     ByVal e As System.EventArgs) Handles cSplit.Click
//003744: 
//003745:         Dim SplitName As String
//003746:         If mFileLoaded = False Then Exit Sub
//003747:         If Len(Trim(tSplitName.Text)) = 0 Then
//003748:             MsgBox("Please specify name for split parts")
//003749:             Exit Sub
//003750:         Else
//003751:             SplitName = Trim(tSplitName.Text)
//003752:         End If
//003753: 
//003754:         'Validation
//003755:         If radTime.Checked Then
//003756:             Dim Duration As Double
//003757:             Duration = numHr.Value * 3600 + numMin.Value * 60 + numSec.Value
//003758:             If Duration > mPlayer.currentMedia.duration Then
//003759:                 MsgBox("Duration cannot be greater than media play time")
//003760:                 Exit Sub
//003761:             End If

//003763:                 MsgBox("Duration should be at least 1 second !!")
//003764:                 Exit Sub
//003765:             End If
//003766:         End If
//003767: 
//003768:         If radPieces.Checked Then
//003769:             If numPcs.Value <= 1 Then
//003770:                 MsgBox("Number of parts required should be more than 1")
//003771:                 Exit Sub
//003772:             End If
//003773:         End If
//003774: 
//003775:         If radSize.Checked Then
//003776:             Dim Value As Integer = CInt(Val(cbSize.Text))
//003777:             If Value <= 0 Then
//003778:                 MsgBox("Please use non-zero numeric values")
//003779:                 Exit Sub
//003780:             End If
//003781:             AddToList(Value)
//003782:         End If
//003783: 
//003784:         'Running the split
//003785:         mainTabs.SelectedTab = tabTrace
//003786:         rtfTrace.SelectedText = vbCrLf
//003787:         statMain.Text = mTranslator.LangText(72)
//003788:         If chkKeepMRU.Checked Then rtfTrace.Clear()
//003789: 
//003790:         Dim Result As Boolean
//003791:         If radTime.Checked Then
//003792:             Dim Duration As Double
//003793:             Duration = numHr.Value * 3600 + numMin.Value * 60 + numSec.Value
//003794:             Result = mHandler.Split(SplitName, Duration, mPlayer.currentMedia.duration)
//003795:         End If
//003796:         If radPieces.Checked Then
//003797:             Result = mHandler.Split(SplitName, CShort(numPcs.Value), _
//003798:             mPlayer.currentMedia.duration)
//003799:         End If
//003800:         If radSize.Checked Then
//003801:             Result = mHandler.Split(SplitName, CInt(Val(cbSize.Text)))
//003802:         End If
//003803: 
//003804:         If Result Then
//003805:             UpdateRTF(vbCrLf & "Success !" & vbCrLf, modMain.MessageType.Success)
//003806:             ShowProcessStat(modMain.MessageType.Success)
//003807:         Else
//003808:             UpdateRTF(vbCrLf & "Failure !" & vbCrLf, modMain.MessageType.Failure)
//003809:             ShowProcessStat(modMain.MessageType.Failure)
//003810:         End If
//003811:         statMain.Text = mTranslator.LangText(23)
//003812:         If chkBeep.Checked Then Beep()
//003813: 
//003814:     End Sub
//003815: 
//003816:     Private Sub AddToList(ByVal Value As Integer)
//003817:         For Each i As Object In cbSize.Items
//003818:             If DirectCast(i, Integer) = Value Then Exit Sub
//003819:         Next

//003860: 
//003861:     Private Sub UpdateEstSize()
//003862: 
//003863:         If mHandler Is Nothing Then Exit Sub
//003864:         If mPlayer.openState <> WMPLib.WMPOpenState.wmposMediaOpen Then Exit Sub
//003865: 
//003866:         Dim fi As New FileInfo(mHandler.InputFile)
//003867:         Dim FileSize As Long = fi.Length
//003868:         Dim EstSize As Double
//003869: 
//003870:         If radTime.Checked Then
//003871:             Dim Duration As Double
//003872:             Duration = numHr.Value * 3600 + numMin.Value * 60 + numSec.Value
//003873:             If Duration > mPlayer.currentMedia.duration Then
//003874:                 EstSize = FileSize / 1024
//003875:             Else
//003876:                 EstSize = (Duration / mPlayer.currentMedia.duration) * (FileSize / 1024)
//003877:             End If
//003878:         End If
//003879: 
//003880:         If radPieces.Checked Then
//003881:             If numPcs.Value = 0 Then Exit Sub
//003882:             EstSize = (FileSize / numPcs.Value) / 1024
//003883:         End If
//003884: 
//003885:         If radSize.Checked Then
//003886:             If Len(cbSize.Text) = 0 Then
//003887:                 EstSize = 0
//003888:             Else
//003889:                 EstSize = Val(cbSize.Text)
//003890:                 If EstSize > FileSize / 1024 Then EstSize = FileSize / 1024
//003891:             End If
//003892:         End If
//003893: 
//003894:         lSize.Text = CStr(CInt(EstSize)) + " kb"
//003895: 
//003896:     End Sub

  .method public instance string  GetString(string Section,

                                            string Default) cil managed
  {

    .maxstack  6

//000039:     Public Function GetString(ByVal Section As String, _
    IL_0000:  nop
//000040:       ByVal Key As String, ByVal [Default] As String) As String
//000041:         ' Returns a string from your INI file
//000042:         Dim intCharCount As Integer
//000043:         Dim objResult As New System.Text.StringBuilder(256)

    IL_0006:  newobj     instance void [mscorlib]System.Text.StringBuilder::.ctor(int32)
    IL_000b:  stloc.2
